      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent review of model setup, boundary conditions, and material assignments by a second analyst.",
      "rationale": "An independent analyst reviewed all model inputs, boundary condition definitions, and material property assignments against the study protocol. Two minor discrepancies in contact stiffness scaling were identified and corrected prior to final simulation runs."
