      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Justification provided for continuum elastic model form; sensitivity to plasticity model documented.",
      "rationale": "Linear elastic model form is justified for the stiffness QoI. For yield force and post-yield response, a bilinear isotropic hardening plasticity model was applied to titanium alloy regions. Sensitivity analysis confirmed that elastic modulus and yield strength are the dominant material parameters; model form uncertainty was quantified and included in uval."
    },
    {
