      "rationale": "Validation activities were conducted on the identical non-cannulated 7.5 mm design under the identical ASTM F1717 compression-bending protocol as the COU. Material, geometry, and loading mode are fully matched. The supplementary plausibility comparison against cannulated historical data (see validation results) was noted as corroborating but was not used to satisfy this factor, as the cannulated geometry constitutes a different structural configuration."
